snippet.title: Official Star Wars™: Battle Pod™ The Force Awakens "Takodana" Trailer
snippet.description: Led by Kylo Ren, the First Order has launched an attack on Maz Kanata’s castle to retrieve the secret map to Luke Skywalker’s location. Knowing this, Poe Dameron leads an elite squad of Resistance fighters in order to stop the First Order.
